Meet Bikram and Prahb from Ferguson Plarre Bakehouses at Fountain Gate shopping centre as they take you through their journey as members of the Ferguson Plarre business and tell us what they love about this 117 year old family business
"This franchise is super supportive, fun and honest. It is not just a franchise but its a family and we all work together to make something special" -

"The brand is well established and offers huge amounts of support. You never feel like you're in this alone because they give you someone to lean on. But they also let you have the independence to own your own business." -
"Easy to manage systems and processes with good support network. Good for someone who is getting into business for first time" -
"Ferguson Plarre has family values & are very passionate about their old fashioned recipes."
"The relationships and access to the Franchisor are second to none. Assistance with promotional work through our support managers, amazing product and viable business sustainability." -
Excellent products, good forward thinking management, market leader, honest franchisor -
The products on offer have a high reputation amongst the community. I get good support from my business coach, and great support from leading barista trainers -
